data.description:
Nestled in a desirable and picturesque mature subdivision, this immaculate 4-bedroom, 2-bathroom residence is a true gem waiting to become your home. As you step through the front door, you'll be greeted by a sense of warmth and space that only a home like this can provide.
The heart of this home is the expansive family room, where an inviting fireplace takes center stage, ready to bring warmth and ambiance to your evenings. See more... This spacious family room creates an open and inviting atmosphere for entertaining friends and family.
The kitchen is spacious with ample counter space, stainless steel appliances, and a layout that will make preparing meals a breeze. Whether you're hosting a dinner party or simply enjoying a quiet breakfast, the kitchen offers the perfect backdrop.
Wonderful laundry room with plenty of extra cabinets, shelving and counterspace. 
An Oasis Awaits outside, you'll discover a lush backyard that's nothing short of a dream. A sizable deck provides a fantastic spot for BBQing, lounging in the sun, or simply unwinding in the serene surroundings. For cozy evenings, a charming firepit beckons, creating the perfect atmosphere for storytelling and making memories under the stars.
This 4-bedroom home in a mature subdivision is an absolute dream. Offering a spacious family room with a fireplace, a well-appointed kitchen, and a backyard that is sure to become your paradise, it's a rare opportunity for both comfortable living and joyful entertaining. Don't miss out on making this house your forever home!
